Description: Two novel methods for network meta-analysis: Ensemble NMA (E-NMA)
    resolves inconsistency via multi-method consensus and adaptive variance
    inflation; Spectral NMA (S-NMA) detects inconsistency via graph Laplacian
    eigen-decomposition. Includes a simulation engine with 10+ network
    topologies, a method evaluator, and 121 curated NMA datasets.
